Usage: vcpe logs [flags]

Surfaces the recent operation timeline. With --name, includes per-deployment log context from the container runtime.

Optional flags:
  --name <deployment>     Show logs scoped to the named deployment
  --state-root <path>     Override the default state root directory
  --json                  Emit structured JSON with timeline and runtimeInitDiagnostics keys

Examples:
  vcpe logs
  vcpe logs --name bng-7
  vcpe logs --name bng-7 --json
